Being a paladin is not about dealing (melee) damage, the DMG of the defender isn't a big deal.<br>
The really nice bits of my epic are:<br>
1. Being able to bash with it without any special AA abilities (You can bash with the Fiery Avenger as well), the paladin epic is a 2H sword and a shield combined.<br>
2. The proc, wich is a fire based stun.<br>
3. The extra stats and resists.<br>
4. The appearance <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The stun proc and bash is worth far more than any extra melee damage i can deal. Paladins prevent and repair damage, we are opposites of the Shadowknights, who are good at inflicting damage.<br>
