I also see Epics as they are now as not equal in terms of their usefulness. If i needed choose between working on my epic...or on the epic of a cleric friend....cleric would get epic first...if only for the clicky rezz.......which is clearly very desireable and useful. Generally speaking though.....if yer in places like the elemental planes....I ahve heard of weapons dropping there that are better then the epic for yer class...so.....it becomes a matter of whether u want yer epic or not.....thats all.  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=614863" target="top"> -- Tiline D'Olath -- </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
